<h2 class="fw-bold">

What is a Rotary Hammer?

</h2>

<p>

A rotary hammer combines a powerful rotation mechanism with pneumatic
hammering action. Unlike a conventional impact drill, it uses compressed air
inside the mechanism to deliver much stronger blows while drilling into hard
materials.

</p>

