<hr class="my-5">

<h2 class="fw-bold">

What is a Demolition Hammer?

</h2>

<p>

A demolition hammer is built for one purpose—breaking materials. Unlike a
rotary hammer, it has <strong>no drilling rotation</strong>. Every bit of the
motor's energy is converted into powerful hammer blows, making it ideal for
heavy demolition.

</p>

